data.description: Surround yourself with nature in beautiful River Pines! This two bedroom two and a half bathroom two story townhome is only steps away from the intracoastal waterway! River Pines backs up to Seabranch Preserve and St. Lucie Inlet Preserve State Park allowing you to enjoy clear starry nights and outdoor adventures. New Mansard to be installed this spring, Interior paint, Kitchen Sink & Disposal, Vertical blinds, Washer & Dryer, Water Heater all new 2022, New A/C 10/21. Western Exposure, Two assigned parking spots, Amenities include: 2 pools, tennis, racquetball, walkway to day dock overlooking the intracoastal as well as a private beach area/Kayak launch with optional assigned storage for boards. Owners can opt in to Miles Grant Golf, No Leases for the first three years, All ages welcome!
